---
import BoxContent from "@/components/box/content.astro";
import BoxHeader from "@/components/box/header.astro";
import Box from "@/components/box/index.astro";
import BoxTitle from "@/components/box/title.astro";
import Footer from "@/components/footer.astro";
import Navbar from "@/components/navbar/index.astro";
import Pattern from "@/components/ui/pattern.astro";
import Layout from "@/layouts/layout.astro";
import { SITE } from "@/lib/config";
import { PROFILE_INFO } from "@/lib/constants/profile";

const title = "Privacy & Cookie Policy";
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <Navbar />
  <Pattern className="h-14" />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl flex-1" aria-label="Main content">
    <Box>
      <BoxHeader>
        <BoxTitle className="text-2xl !font-black">Privacy & Cookie Policy</BoxTitle>
      </BoxHeader>
      <BoxContent>
        <section class="prose max-w-none">
          <h2>Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            This site is a personal portfolio operated by <strong>{PROFILE_INFO.displayName}</strong>. The site does not
            require accounts, newsletters, or payments and does not intentionally collect personally identifiable
            information beyond standard technical data required for site operation and analytics.
          </p>

          <h2>Data controller</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>Controller:</strong>
            {PROFILE_INFO.displayName}<br />
            <strong>Contact:</strong>
            <a href={`mailto:${PROFILE_INFO.email}`}>{PROFILE_INFO.email}</a><br />
            <strong>Site:</strong>
            <a href={`${SITE.profile}`}>{SITE.profile}</a>
          </p>

          <h2>What data may be technically processed</h2>
          <p>
            Although the site does not ask for personal data, standard technical data may be processed automatically
            when you visit, including:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Server logs (IP address, request path, timestamp, HTTP status)</li>
            <li>Browser and device information (user agent, screen size, language)</li>
            <li>Referrer and click data (which pages you visited and where you came from)</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            These items are used for site operation, security, and anonymous analytics and are not used to build user
            profiles or for targeted advertising.
          </p>

          <h2>Hosting and infrastructure</h2>
          <p>
            This website is hosted on <a href="https://vercel.com">Vercel</a> and served via a CDN. Vercel may process server
            logs and aggregated analytics on my behalf. Their systems may handle IP addresses and request metadata necessary
            for delivery, performance, and basic analytics. See Vercel's privacy documentation for details.
          </p>

          <h2>Cookies</h2>
          <p>This site is intentionally minimal and does not rely on non-essential cookies for core functionality.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Site cookies:</strong> If you do not interact with embedded third-party content, this site should not
              set persistent cookies.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Vercel Analytics:</strong> Vercel Analytics is privacy-focused and does not rely on browser cookies;
              it collects aggregated, anonymous metrics (page views, performance) and does not create personal profiles or
              set third-party marketing cookies.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Third-party embeds:</strong> Embedded content (e.g., videos or widgets) may set cookies from those
              third parties. This policy does not cover those cookies.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            <strong>Controlling cookies:</strong> You can control or delete cookies in your browser settings. Blocking cookies
            may affect functionality on other sites, but this portfolio is designed to remain usable.
          </p>

          <h2>Third-party services</h2>
          <p>The site uses the following third-party services:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Vercel</strong> — hosting, CDN, and optional analytics. (<a
                href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy">Vercel Privacy</a
              >)
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Google Search Console / Site Verification</strong> — used only to verify site ownership and monitor
              search performance; it does not affect normal visitors. (<a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
                >Google Privacy</a
              >)
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2>GDPR and your rights</h2>
          <p>If you are in the EU/EEA, you have rights over personal data, including:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request confirmation of processing and a copy of personal data.</li>
            <li><strong>Rectification:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
            <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request deletion where there is no lawful reason to retain data.</li>
            <li><strong>Restriction:</strong> Request temporary suspension of processing.</li>
            <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Request a copy of data you provided in a machine-readable format.</li>
            <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to processing where permitted by law.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            To exercise these rights, email me. Because this site collects minimal data, many requests will be satisfied
            by confirming that no personal data is held.
          </p>

          <h2>Data retention</h2>
          <p>
            Retention periods for server logs and analytics are determined by hosting and analytics providers. I retain
            the minimum necessary to run, secure, and maintain the site. Contact me for specifics or to request deletion
            of data I control.
          </p>

          <h2>Security</h2>
          <p>
            I apply reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect data. No system is perfectly secure.
          </p>

          <h2>External links</h2>
          <p>
            This site may link to third-party sites. I am not responsible for their privacy practices or content. Review
            their policies before providing personal information.
          </p>

          <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>
            I may update this policy occasionally. The version on this page is current; check the page date where
            available.
          </p>

          <h2>Cookie-specific statement</h2>
          <p>
            This website does not rely on cookies for core functionality. This site does not intentionally use
            non-essential cookies. I will update this policy if I add features that use cookies.
          </p>

          <h2>Compliance note</h2>
          <p>
            Under GDPR, a consent banner is typically required for non-essential cookies. Because this site uses only
            privacy-friendly analytics (Vercel) and avoids marketing cookies, a consent banner is generally not
            required; a clear privacy page is recommended. If you add typical analytics or third-party embeds that set
            cookies, you should add a consent mechanism.
          </p>
        </section>
      </BoxContent>
    </Box>
  </main>
  <Pattern />
  <Footer />
</Layout>
